ActNational Capital Act
SubjectExtension of lease between NCC and Vivid Contracting Inc.
PrecisOrder approving that the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION grant three options to extend the lease with VIVID CONTRACTING INC. for the real property located at 225 Slack Road, in Ottawa, Ontario, for a period of 5 years each, beginning on October 1, 2025, October 1, 2030 and October 1, 2035.
